.fi
.TP
.B Options
.RS 4
.B \-t, \-\-tag <tag>
optional: Filter commits by tag name.
.RE
.RS 4
.B \-d, \-\-date <YYYY\-MM\-DD>
optional: Filter commits by local date prefix.
.RE
.TP
.B Examples
.nf
omohi find
omohi find \-\-tag release
omohi find \-\-date 2026\-03\-17
omohi find \-\-tag release \-\-date 2026\-03\-17
.fi
.TP
.B Notes
.RS 4
When both filters are set, intersection is returned.
.RE
